query:
ALTER TABLE projects 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS designLife INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS endOfLifeDate TIMESTAMP NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS holdingDepartment VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS propertyManager VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS managerEmail VARCHAR(320),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS managerPhone VARCHAR(50),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS facilityType VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS occupancyStatus ENUM('occupied', 'vacant', 'partial'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS criticalityLevel ENUM('critical', 'important', 'standard');
